                     <interp inst="t17751206-1-person130" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             the next day on his, was to throw the blame, as much as they could, upon Mrs. Rudd, and from thence to infer their having been imposed upon: now I ask,<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177512060011"></xptr> how it came to pass that Cassidy, in neither of the trials, nor you in the trial of 
               <persName id="t17751206-1-person131">
                  Daniel
