                  </persName>
            , whether this prisoner was that Mrs. Porter or Potter that had lived at Hackney? - I did.</p>
               <p>Did you enquire of any woman? - I believe there were two women.</p>
               <p>Of Mrs. 
               <persName id="t17751206-1-person164">
