                     <interp inst="t17751206-1-person171" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             one of the two women you mentioned speaking to at Hackney, or is she a third woman? - She was not one of those two women I spoke to at Hackney.</p>
               <p>Counsel for the Crown. Sir Thomas, look at that draught again. I see there are some blots upon the face of it; do you remember whether these blots were upon it when you gave it to 
               <persName id="t17751206-1-person172">
