            's: I assisted him in his business of an apothecary.</p>
               <p>Do you remember seeing Mrs. Rudd there? - Very frequently.</p>
               <p>What time did you see her there upon Christmas day 1774? - From about seven in the evening till about ten.</p>
               <p>Did you see her on the 24th? - Yes.</p>
               <p>Did she say any thing to you? - Not in particular: she expressed a great deal of inclination for 
               <persName id="t17751206-1-person184">
                  Robert
                   Perreau
               <interp inst="t17751206-1-person184" type="surname" value="Perreau"></interp>
