                     <interp inst="t17751206-1-person186" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            's coming home? - Yes, in a very short time after the messenger returned; ten or twelve minutes.</p>
               <p>Was you present at any conversation when Mr. 
               <persName id="t17751206-1-person187">
                  Robert
                   Perreau
               <interp inst="t17751206-1-person187" type="surname" value="Perreau"></interp>
