                     <interp inst="t17751206-1-person187" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             returned? - No: I withdrew, supposing Mrs. Rudd had business with him.</p>
               <p>Cross Examination.</p>
               <p>Are you privy to the transactions of the Perreaus in the stocks? - No.</p>
               <p>Mr. Davenport. I beg to ask Sir 
               <persName id="t17751206-1-person188">
