                     <interp inst="t17751206-1-person196" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             wanted such sums of money? - That was best known to himself.</p>
               <p>Then I am to understand you, that, upon your oath, you have never searched the books for 
               <persName id="t17751206-1-person197">
                  Robert
