                  </persName>
            's dealings in the stocks? - I never have, I declare upon my oath.</p>
               <p>Then I am misinformed; I had heard so. - I have searched the Bank for the bank notes, and I have traced them.</p>
               <p>Counsel. That is not what I mean: I mean settling differences.</p>
