               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177512060017"></xptr>Did he pay in any money on the 26th of December? - Yes; 4000 l. in bank notes; there were three notes of a 1000 l. each, one for 800 l. two for 50 l. each, a 40 l. a 30 l. a 20 l. and a 10 l. note: I have a paper containing the marks and numbers, &amp;c. of the notes which I extracted from the book (producing it.).</p>
