               <p>What balance was there in his favour at the end of the month? - 483 l. 6 s.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17751206-1-person209">
                  JOHN
                   MOODY
               <interp inst="t17751206-1-person209" type="surname" value="MOODY"></interp>
