                     <interp inst="t17751206-1-person230" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            's in March? - I did.</p>
               <p>Did you then disclose it to him? - Never.</p>
               <p>Was you before Sir 
               <persName id="t17751206-1-person231">
                  John
                   Fielding
               <interp inst="t17751206-1-person231" type="surname" value="Fielding"></interp>
