                     <interp inst="t17751206-1-person238" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             had been in New Prison? - About a fortnight.</p>
               <p>Was that the first you had heard of 
               <persName id="t17751206-1-person239">
                  Daniel
                   Perreau
               <interp inst="t17751206-1-person239" type="surname" value="Perreau"></interp>
