                     <interp inst="t17751206-1-person247" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , did not come from Mr. 
               <persName id="t17751206-1-person248">
                  William
                   Adair
               <interp inst="t17751206-1-person248" type="surname" value="Adair"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17751206-1-person248" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17751206-1-person248" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            ? - I did not, I told him I would disclose to his attorney all I knew of the matter.</p>
               <p>And then you did not disclose that to him at all? - I did not at all.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17751206-1-person249">
                  THOMAS
                   ALEXANDER
               <interp inst="t17751206-1-person249" type="surname" value="ALEXANDER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17751206-1-person249" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17751206-1-person249" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>You knew Mr. 
               <persName id="t17751206-1-person250">
                  Daniel
